Name: Box End Roll Cage
Description: Box end part acts as half tube clamp and adds roll cage for protection and mounting.
Notes: Typically paired with Box End square on top of frame ends.  Also holds GPS and other mounts above frame.

Name: Box End Rounded
Description: Box end part acts as half tube clamp and is usually used on bottom of box end.  Rounded outside corners avoid sharp edges.
Notes: Typically paired with Box End Square on bottom of frame ends.

Name: Box End Square
Description: Box end parts acts as tube half clamp and is used in middle of box end.
Notes: Typically paired with Box End Roll Cage and Box End Rounded to form frame end tube clamps
